data.name: label1.Text
data.value: Hello, My name is Mr. Skulleton. I come from a rather boring place. You see, everyone on my planet including me is dead. So I decided to leave my planet and visit other places. Get to know other species. I'm not sure for how long I traveled. I had this god awful song stuck in my head. Couldn't get it out. Anyway look at me blabering around Where was I? Ah yes. So I want to have fun and have compiled the list of the most played game in your world. So what do you say? Can we play?

data.name: label2.Text
data.value: Are you kidding me? I've been traveling for ages. You can't say no and why are you being rude? It's not stupid games. I've traveled through galaxy to play them. Besides I might have your friend locked up, you'll have to find out.
